* Imgur Mushroom

This is Image file uploader for Imgur image sharing service.
NOTICE: this app require other app that work as image picker.

** feature
- Imgur account and album supported. (upload only, no browse function)
- and also, this app has in-app upload history. you can delete the image from server with/without account.
- If start as Mushroom(IME extension), automatically input the URL that link to uploaded image.
- or start as standalone, automatically copy the URL to clipboard.
- or start with "share intent" from other apps.
- In-app image editor supported. resize, rotate, crop, convert PNG to JPEG.
- Android OS 1.6 supported.
- This app is open-source. https://github.com/tateisu/imgur-upload-mushroom

** tested hardware
- Galaxy S2(docomo SC-02C)
- Galaxy Nexus(docomo SC-04D)
- Motorola XOOM2 MZ615
- Huawei IDEOS
- IS01

